UniCredit’s HVB to Outsource Service Units, FT Deutschland Says

-- B y   R i c h a r d   W e i s s
-- 
2011-08-22T05:46:58Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-22/unicredit-s-hvb-to-outsource-service-units-ft-deutschland-says.html
HVB Group,  UniCredit SpA (UCG) ’s German
banking unit, plans to outsource service units including
procurement, the operation of computer systems and real estate
management,  Financial Times Deutschland  said, citing an
interview with board member Heinz Laber.  The units will be bundled in a new company called UniCredit
Global Business Services GmbH based in Munich, which will have
up to 3,000 employees and start operating on Nov. 1, the
newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
 Richard Weiss  in Frankfurt at 
 rweiss5@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Benedikt Kammel at   bkammel@bloomberg.net . 